                              boolean universalRestriction)
        Creates a new relationship backing bean with the specified arguments.
        Parameters:
        model - the relationship's originating model (may not be null)
        sctId - the relationship's SNOMED CT identifier; a value of UNINITIALIZED indicates a new relationship
        released - true if the represented component is released. Otherwise false.
        universalRestriction - flag indicating the DL restriction for the relationship. true if universal restriction, otherwise false.
